{"tid":752551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[社團 - Verein]德領事館「每週一字」再暗諷香港政治事","createTime":"2018-07-23T02:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T02:08:06.000Z","uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"78e7636283492f599aaa5508d45243e150b0b148","tid":752551,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T02:08:06.000Z","msg":"德國駐香港總領事館facebook專頁「每週一字」教授德文欄目，素來喜歡因應中港政治事件借題發揮。今天發佈的「每週一字」為「社團（Verein）」，例句為「社團裡活動不那麼多」，似是諷刺香港政府以《社團條例》擬取締香港民族黨一事。<br />\n<br />\n德國駐香港總領事館上星期六的「每週一字」教導「自由」的德文「Freiheit」，並有例句「自由無價」，也是明顯呼應劉霞獲准離京前赴德國柏林，重獲自由。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/GERMAN-WORD-ASSOC_UyGTN_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FGERMAN-WORD-ASSOC_UyGTN_1200x0.png&h=a7c7ae54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發音/Pronunciation: <a href=\"http://www.dict.cc/?s=Verein\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dict.cc%2F%3Fs%3DVerein&d=7zgpRuyat%2F7NDD5N4EVKjP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=c2ba48ea\" target=\"_blank\">www.dict.cc/?s=Verein</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/36989035_876872615846191_5886863359092981760_n.png?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=18582168703da035e7c834f779b29866&amp;oe=5BDF7B5A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F36989035_876872615846191_5886863359092981760_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3D18582168703da035e7c834f779b29866%26oe%3D5BDF7B5A&h=08830f67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%BE%B7%E9%A0%98%E4%BA%8B%E9%A4%A8-%E6%AF%8F%E9%80%B1%E4%B8%80%E5%AD%97-%E5%86%8D%E6%9A%97%E8%AB%B7%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E4%BA%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E9%25A0%2598%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E6%25AF%258F%25E9%2580%25B1%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AD%2597-%25E5%2586%25